          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2013-04-26T16:45:59Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Ensuring Proper Community Investments Act of 2013 - Amends the Housing and Community Development Act of 1974 to prohibit a metropolitan city, urban county, local government, Indian tribe, or insular area that receives a community development block grant from the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development (HUD), or through a state allocation, from selling, trading, or otherwise transferring all or any portion of such grant to or for any other such entity.</p>]]></text>
